# .NET Development Guidelines

## Architecture
- Follow Clean Architecture principles
- Implement proper dependency injection
- Use proper middleware
- Follow CQRS pattern where appropriate
- Implement proper logging

## API Design
- Follow RESTful principles
- Use proper versioning
- Implement proper authentication/authorization
- Use proper response types
- Follow proper error handling

## Entity Framework
- Use proper DbContext patterns
- Implement proper migrations
- Use proper lazy loading
- Follow proper repository pattern
- Implement proper unit of work

## Security
- Implement proper authentication
- Use proper authorization
- Follow proper security headers
- Implement proper input validation
- Use proper encryption

## Performance
- Use proper caching
- Implement proper async/await
- Use proper connection pooling
- Follow proper optimization patterns
- Implement proper memory management

## Testing
- Write unit tests
- Implement integration tests
- Use proper mocking
- Follow proper testing patterns
- Implement proper test data